- [packages/ui/src/lib/](mdc:packages/ui/src/lib) - Utility functions and helpers
- [packages/ui/src/card.tsx](mdc:packages/ui/src/card.tsx) - Card component
- [packages/ui/src/gradient.tsx](mdc:packages/ui/src/gradient.tsx) - Gradient component
